Interface IBMECMBaseObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IBMECMBaseObject>, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBMECMAttributeDefinition, IBMECMBaseUser, IBMECMComment, IBMECMContentClass, IBMECMContentItem, IBMECMDesktop, IBMECMDirectory, IBMECMFavorite, IBMECMItem, IBMECMRepository, IBMECMSearchCriteria, IBMECMSearchRepository, IBMECMSearchTemplate, IBMECMSocialItem, IBMECMSyncChange, IBMECMSyncItem, IBMECMTeamspace, IBMECMUser, IBMECMUserGroup, IBMECMUserRole

    public interface IBMECMBaseObject
extends Serializable, Comparable<IBMECMBaseObject>
    Represents the base class that provides the id and name of an object, or item, that other items extend from.

      • getCacheProperty

        Object getCacheProperty(String propertyName)
        Returns a value for the cache property for this base item. This cache property is not persisted onto the IBM Content Navigator server. It is only for temporary storage.
        Parameters:
        propertyName - the name of the property to cache
        Returns:
        the value of the cache property. It will return null if this property was never cached before.
